# Security Rules

Follow [`docs/security.md`](../../docs/security.md) and [`docs/authentication.md`](../../docs/authentication.md).

- Fail closed on auth and validation errors.
- Validate at API ingress (Zod); reject unknown fields on strict schemas.
- bcrypt for passwords; JWT access token 15m; refresh via HttpOnly cookie.
- Never commit secrets; never expose stack traces or R2 internals in API errors.
- Rate-limit auth and write endpoints.
